  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shadow Alchemist is an isometric pixel art game that blends puzzle-solving and reality-bending alchemy. Awaken in the depths of a shadowy dungeon, you'll embark on a journey of self-discovery and transformation that challenges your perception of reality itself.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Alchemical Abilities</strong>: Master the art of self-transmutation, unlocking powers that allow you to become invincible, shrink to minuscule sizes, and even create duplicate of yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294930/extras/a97a3387ae017bdb94956e4f49fa2563.poster.avif?t=1733082373\" width=609 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294930/extras/a97a3387ae017bdb94956e4f49fa2563.webm?t=1733082373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mind-Bending Puzzles</strong>: Navigate through increasingly complex environmental challenges that require creative use of your alchemical abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294930/extras/af88db1476f454455bb7cdbac10559f0.poster.avif?t=1733082373\" width=609 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294930/extras/af88db1476f454455bb7cdbac10559f0.webm?t=1733082373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Light Combat</strong>: Engage in occasional skirmishes with wandering enemies, or use your wit and timing to avoid confrontation altogether.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294930/extras/889a35c26ebb6278a517ad71b05a833d.poster.avif?t=1733082373\" width=609 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294930/extras/889a35c26ebb6278a517ad71b05a833d.webm?t=1733082373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Recursive Mystery</strong>: Experience a narrative that evolves with each \"escape,\" as subtle changes in the dungeon and your own memories hint at a greater truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you delve deeper into the dungeon's secrets, you'll uncover startling truths about your own nature and the reality that surrounds you. Can you master the alchemical abilites, overcome the challenges, and ultimately unravel the mystery of your past?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shadow Alchemist is an isometric pixel art game that blends puzzle-solving and reality-bending alchemy. Awaken in the depths of a shadowy dungeon, you'll embark on a journey of self-discovery and transformation that challenges your perception of reality itself.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Alchemical Abilities</strong>: Master the art of self-transmutation, unlocking powers that allow you to become invincible, shrink to minuscule sizes, and even create duplicate of yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294930/extras/a97a3387ae017bdb94956e4f49fa2563.poster.avif?t=1733082373\" width=609 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294930/extras/a97a3387ae017bdb94956e4f49fa2563.webm?t=1733082373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mind-Bending Puzzles</strong>: Navigate through increasingly complex environmental challenges that require creative use of your alchemical abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294930/extras/af88db1476f454455bb7cdbac10559f0.poster.avif?t=1733082373\" width=609 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294930/extras/af88db1476f454455bb7cdbac10559f0.webm?t=1733082373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul c